Node:	wave_greeting (Speech response to waving gesture)
Input:
	uint8 gesture[]
Config:
	enum GestureType {
		RIGHT_SWIPE = 0x01,
		LEFT_SWIPE = 0x02,
		NO_GESTURE = 0xFF
	}
	uint16 sum (sum of pairs within the gesture input list)
Output:
	None
Steps:
	1. Initialization: Begin subscribing to tpc_gesture (10Hz)
	2. if sum value equals 0x03
		(a) Send request to srv_speaker ("Hello").
